# Core

The mission of the core team is to steer Gratipay as a whole in pursuit of our
overall [mission](http://inside.gratipay.com/big-picture/mission): to cultivate
an economy of gratitude, generosity, and love.

## Scope

Anything not explicitly in scope for another team falls to the core team.

- [Mission](http://inside.gratipay.com/big-picture/mission) and [Brand](http://inside.gratipay.com/big-picture/brand/)
- Strategy
- Governance
- repos:
  - https://github.com/gratipay/inside.gratipay.com
  - https://github.com/gratipay/bot
  - https://github.com/gratipay/access-dashboard
  - https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay-queue-dashboard

# Marketing

The mission of the marketing team is to communicate with the market, listening
for problems relevant to our organizational mission, and sharing our solutions.

## Scope

- https://gratipay.news/
- social media:
  - https://twitter.com/Gratipay
  - https://www.facebook.com/Gratipay
- [Events](https://github.com/gratipay/inside.gratipay.com/labels/Events)
- repos:
  - https://github.com/gratipay/guide
  - https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay-or-bountysource.guide
  - https://github.com/gratipay/blog.gittip.com

# Support

The mission of the support team is to help people use our products.

## Scope

- support@gratipay.com
- the [Support](https://gratipay.freshdesk.com/helpdesk/tickets/view/1000240520) and [L2 Support](https://gratipay.freshdesk.com/helpdesk/tickets/view/1000241179) queues in Freshdesk
- https://github.com/gratipay/team-review

# Product

The mission of the product team is to design and implement solutions to the
problems identified by the marketing team.

## Scope

- https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay.com
  - [translation](https://www.transifex.com/gratipay/gratipay/) ([docs](http://inside.gratipay.com/howto/translate-gratipay))
- https://github.com/gratipay/grtp.co
- https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay-everywhere
- https://github.com/gratipay/gratipay-badge

# Accounting

The mission of the accounting team is to account for the money we move.

## Scope

- @gratipay/finances 
- the https://github.com/gratipay/finances repo
- the `statements` directory in the https://github.com/gratipay/logs repo
- the vendors@gratipay.com email address

# Tech

The mission of the tech team is to support the product team in solving problems
in the market.

## Scope

- dev
- ops
- hosting
  - Heroku
  - Digital Ocean
  - AWS
- monitoring
  - Sentry
  - PagerDuty
  - UptimeRobot
  - Librato
- Payday
- https://github.com/gratipay/postgres.py
- https://github.com/gratipay/gip.rocks
- https://github.com/gratipay/honcho
- https://github.com/gratipay/environment.py


# Security

The mission of the security team is to protect our sensitive information.

## Scope

- [our HackerOne account](https://hackerone.com/gratipay)
- the &ldquo;[Handle Security Issues](inside.gratipay.com/howto/handle-security-issues)&rdquo; document
- [`Security Team`](https://github.com/gratipay/inside.gratipay.com/labels/Security%20Team) issues
- the legacy [Hall of Fame](https://gratipay.com/about/security/hall-of-fame) page on gratipay.com
- the @gratipay/security team
- the https://github.com/gratipay/security repo
- the security@gratipay.com email address
